{"tid":176637,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府下周刊憲准小巴增至19座","createTime":"2017-03-28T09:59:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T15:21:26.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3079af593d9ca06219aa3f2ba80cdc0a0cf99fe","tid":176637,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T09:59:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170328/large/1490694651_60a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170328%2Flarge%2F1490694651_60a0.jpg&h=92c5fb5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府公佈，將於下周五（4月7日）刊憲，將小巴（包括公共小巴及私家小巴）座位上限由16個增至19個，以更有效應付尤其在繁忙時段乘客對公共小巴服務的需求。發言人指，小巴上一次增加座位是1988年，當時由原來14座增加至16座，「在決定合適的座位上限時，主要考慮公共小巴服務的供求情況，以及維持各種公共交通服務之間得來不易的生態平衡。將公共小巴的座位上限定為19個的建議，是平衡兩方面考慮因素的最佳安排。政策考慮並不會以個別車款或型號作依據。市場是會按政策轉變而調節作適應。」"},{"pid":"e8806d2e9394172e3a4d4f33b01be0edbe3f82d1","tid":176637,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:02:06.000Z","msg":"安全？"},{"pid":"088370d1eceb0cf6eb5c02cbc5da52c03b2ead7e","tid":176637,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>安全？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搭亡命VAN問安唔安全？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac25a3f58eabe6cf9e3ca479cb291f80148e2195","tid":176637,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T10:09:56.000Z","msg":"紅van等滿座先開咪等到天光"},{"pid":"d5704c57a308397ab144e91d3d485ee5f2fc503e","tid":176637,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"加邊度？"},{"pid":"f65e7bb19c23e89def969a12d7be3528d97a939c","tid":176637,"uid":72621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅van等滿座先開咪等到天光</blockquote><br />\n綠van都成日去到中間等客<br />\n屌<br />\n好似8號仔無人坐既話家維邨又等"},{"pid":"caf517a1cf8716fbea6aba2da35777ddeccd9